---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = '21 June 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Kebijakan privasi Vanillate Studio."
>
  <section class="container-page pt-20 md:pt-28 pb-12 max-w-3xl">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-6">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="font-display font-semibold tracking-tightest text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-tight mb-6">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-ink-500 dark:text-cream-300/60 font-mono">
      Last Updated: {lastUpdated}
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="container-page pb-24 max-w-3xl">
    <div class="space-y-12 text-ink-700 dark:text-cream-200 leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          This Privacy Policy explains how Vanillate ("the Bot", "we", "our", or "us") collects, uses, stores, and protects information necessary to provide its features and services on Discord.
        </p>
        <p>
          By using Vanillate, you agree to the collection and use of information as described in this Privacy Policy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          To provide gameplay features and maintain the operation of the Bot, we may collect and store the following information:
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-3 text-ink-900 dark:text-cream-50">Discord User Data</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-0 list-none mb-6">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Discord User ID</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Username and display name</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Gameplay statistics</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Experience points, levels, achievements, and progression data</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Inventory, currency, and other game-related data</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Leaderboard and ranking information</span></li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-3 text-ink-900 dark:text-cream-50">Discord Server Data</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-0 list-none mb-6">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Discord Server ID</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Channel IDs used for Bot functionality</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Guild-specific configuration settings</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Gameplay-related server data</span></li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-3 text-ink-900 dark:text-cream-50">Technical Data</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-0 list-none mb-6">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Error logs</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Command usage statistics</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Performance and diagnostic information necessary to maintain service reliability</span></li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          We do not collect passwords, payment information, email addresses, direct messages unrelated to Bot functionality, or other sensitive personal information.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">3. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We use collected information solely to operate and improve Vanillate, including:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-0 list-none mb-4">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Providing gameplay functionality</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Saving player progress and achievements</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Maintaining leaderboards and rankings</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Managing guild, economy, and game systems</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Preventing abuse, cheating, fraud, or malicious activity</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Troubleshooting errors and improving performance</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Developing and testing new features</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not use collected data for advertising purposes.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">4. Message Content and Privileged Intents</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Vanillate may process message content and other Discord data only when required for Bot functionality and in accordance with Discord's Developer Terms and Policies.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Message content is processed exclusively to provide requested commands, gameplay interactions, moderation features, or other Bot-related functionality.
        </p>
        <p>We do not sell, share, or use message content for advertising or profiling purposes.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">5. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We do not sell, rent, trade, or otherwise monetize user data.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">Information may only be disclosed:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-0 list-none">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>When required by applicable law or legal process</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>To protect the security, integrity, or operation of the Bot</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>To investigate abuse, fraud, or violations of our policies</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>When necessary to comply with Discord's policies and requirements</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We retain information only for as long as reasonably necessary to provide services and maintain gameplay functionality.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">Data may be deleted when:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-0 list-none mb-4">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>A server removes the Bot</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>A user submits a valid deletion request</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>The data is no longer required for operational purposes</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>We determine that retention is no longer necessary</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Certain records may be retained temporarily for security, abuse prevention, or legal compliance purposes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">7. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect stored information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
        </p>
        <p>
          However, no method of electronic transmission or storage can be guaranteed to be completely secure.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">8. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Vanillate operates through Discord and may utilize third-party hosting, database, analytics, or infrastructure providers to maintain service availability.
        </p>
        <p>
          Use of such services is governed by their respective privacy policies and terms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Vanillate is not intended for individuals who are below the minimum age required to use Discord under applicable laws and Discord's Terms of Service.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">10. User Rights</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Users may request:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-0 list-none mb-4">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Information regarding stored data</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Correction of inaccurate information</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Deletion of eligible data associated with their Discord account</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Clarification regarding how their data is used</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p>Requests may be submitted through our official support server.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">11. Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.</p>
        <p>
          Any changes will become effective upon publication of the updated policy. Continued use of Vanillate after such changes constitutes acceptance of the revised Privacy Policy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">12. Contact</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          For privacy-related inquiries, data requests, or support, contact us through:
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://discord.gg/A7n88d6uRW"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-ink-900 dark:bg-amber-500 text-cream-50 dark:text-ink-950 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform"
        >
          Discord Support Server
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H8M17 7v9" /></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-8 border-t border-ink-900/10 dark:border-cream-100/10">
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-500 dark:text-cream-300/60">
          &copy; 2026 Vanillate. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
